  "time_ut": 1662022994,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The coconut plucked by the father took the life of the son",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Namunukula - Namunukula police said that the son died after a coconut fell on his son's head.",
        "10th standard student of Miyakanandura Maha Vidyalaya, HM Sameera, resident of Miyakanandura, passed away.",
        "On the 29th at 6.30 pm, when the father climbed a 50-feet tall tree in the garden and plucked a coconut, the police said that the investigation revealed that the son was returning home and the coconut was plucked at that time.",
        "He was seriously injured and died yesterday (31) after being admitted to Badulla General Hospital.",
        "The police have mentioned that legal action will be taken against the 55-year-old father on the charge of negligent plucking of coconuts. (R)"
      ],
